{"type":"message","id":"96d25ba8","parentId":"d19d7d30","timestamp":"2026-03-03T13:30:25.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to monitor financial news using QVeris Finnhub, with a热度 (heat/popularity) ≥ 80, and推送 (push) to the user. No browser - must use QVeris only.\n\nThis is a cron job for economy/finance news monitoring. I need to:\n1. Use QVeris to search for Finnhub financial news\n2. Filter for news with heat/popularity ≥ 80\n3. Push relevant news to the user\n\nLet me search for current financial news via QVeris.","thinkingSignature":"38b946105f323e16bbf3274c3fffaaed7af6acc7c66c53bfe5051a5c22bf87a1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ut6gyp4h6g9p_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"finhub financial news market stocks"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":14069,"totalTokens":14259,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772544600063}}
