opularity data from the ‘Explore’ feature of Google Trends. You can check keyword trends for Google Search, Google News, Google Images, Google Shopping, and YouTube.\",\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"device\": \"desktop\",\n          \"date_to\": \"2024-12-31\",\n          \"keywords\": [\n            \"example keyword\"\n          ],\n          \"date_from\": \"2024-01-01\",\n          \"category_code\": 0,\n          \"location_name\": \"United States\",\n          \"time_offset_unit\": \"week\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"DataForSEO provides a comprehensive suite of APIs for SEO, keyword research, SERP data, backlinks, reviews, app stores, business listings, and more. It supports use cases across digital marketing, AI development, ecommerce, and enterprise applications.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 0,\n        \"success_rate\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"x_developer.2.likes.compliance.stream.retrieve.v1.4967071a\",\n      \"name\": \"Stream Likes compliance data\",\n      \"description\": \"Streams all compliance data related to Likes for Users.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"backfill_minutes\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The number of minutes of backfill requested.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"start_time\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ. The earliest UTC timestamp from which the Likes Compliance events will be provided.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"end_time\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ. The latest UTC timestamp from which the Likes Compliance events