{"type":"message","id":"7ecd21a6","parentId":"1b951dfa","timestamp":"2026-03-03T13:37:05.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the data. The Finnhub news doesn't have a \"heat\" score per se, but it does have \"category\" - \"top news\" seems to indicate more important/popular news. \n\nLooking at the data, I can see:\n- category: \"top news\" \n- datetime: Unix timestamp\n- headline, summary, source, url\n\nThe user's request for \"热度≥80\" might be a specific requirement they have. Since Finnhub doesn't provide this metric, I should either:\n1. Inform the user that Finnhub doesn't provide a heat score\n2. Use a proxy like \"top news\" category as high heat\n\nLet me analyze what we have and provide a summary. The news is clearly about:\n- Iran conflict / Middle East\n- Oil prices spiking\n- Treasury yields\n- Stock market movements (Best Buy, SpaceX, Target, etc.)\n- JPMorgan CEO warnings\n- Gold\n\nThese are clearly hot/top news. Let me present this to the user and explain the situation.","thinkingSignature":"ded518953da0844f7ca933558b5c00341fface7e9866a58f480714a8fdd1ab65"},{"type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis, here's the situation:\n\n**Finnhub API 现状:**\n- Finnhub market news 返回的字段包括: `category`, `datetime`, `headline`, `source`, `summary`, `url`\n- **没有提供\"热度\"或\"heat score\"字段**\n- `category: \"top news\"` 可以作为高热度新闻的标志\n\n**当前热门财经新闻 (来自Finnhub):**\n\n| 时间 | 标题 | 来源 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Iran冲突升级 | \"Trump has less than 30 days to end the Iran conflict or he'll lose his inflation battle\" | MarketWatch |\n| 油价飙升 | \"Oil prices surge to highest in a year as fears of Middle East supply crunch grow\" | MarketWatch |\n| 黄金测试 | \"Gold just passed its stress test — what happens next will tell investors if they're right\" | MarketWatch |\n| JPM预警 | \"JPMorgan's Jamie Dimon warns there's too much complacency in markets\" | MarketWatch |\n| 美债大跌 | \"Bonds head for biggest selloff in nine months as Iran conflict sparks unusual Treasury moves\" | MarketWatch |\n| 韩国股市 | \"World's hottest stock market suddenly blows cold with a 7% tumble\" | MarketWatch |\n| Nvidia升级 | \"We're upgrading our rating on Nvidia shares\" | CNBC |\n| SpaceX IPO | \"SpaceX's stock could trade like Tesla 'on steroids' after IPO\" | MarketWatch |\n\n---\n\n由于Finnhub API本身**不提供热度数值评分**，无法直接筛选\"热度≥80\"的新闻。目前数据均为\"top news\"类别（可视为高热度）。\n\n**请问:**\n1. 是否需要改用其他提供热度评分的数据源?\n2. 或者您对\"热度\"有其他定义标准?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":40801,"output":580,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772545006055}}
